#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: nya24, sc79
msgctxt "mn38:24.1"
msgid "“Api nu tumhe, bhikkhave, evaṃ jānantā evaṃ passantā etarahi vā paccuppannamaddhānaṃ ajjhattaṃ kathaṅkathī assatha—"
msgstr "“Knowing and seeing in this way, mendicants, would you be undecided about the present, thinking, "

# NOTE: The shift to singular seems unjustified.
msgctxt "mn38:24.2"
msgid "ahaṃ nu khosmi, no nu khosmi, kiṃ nu khosmi, kathaṃ nu khosmi, ayaṃ nu kho satto kuto āgato, so kuhiṃ gāmī bhavissatī”ti? "
